<h3>Plugin Usage</h3>

<p>Find a versioned CSS file.</p>
<code>
    <pre>
{{ '<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ manifest(\'css/main.css\') }}">' | e }}
    </pre>
</code>

<p>Find a versioned JavaScript file.</p>
<code>
    <pre>
{{ '<script src="{{ manifest(\'js/main.js\') }}"></script>' | e }}
    </pre>
</code>

<p>Lazily find a versioned file and build the tag based on the file extension.</p>
<code>
    <pre>
{{ '{{ manifest(\'js/main.js\', true) | raw }}' | e }}
    </pre>
</code>

<p>Alternatively include the content of a versioned file inline.</p>
<code>
    <pre>
{{ '{{ manifest(\'css/main.css\', true, true) | raw }}' | e }}
    </pre>
</code>
